Processing Decades Data
=======================

Screen layout:

----------------------------------------
(Menus) File: Modules: Parameters: Process: Help
----------------------------------------

   (View of Files/Modules/Parameters)
  

----------------------------------------


               ( Log )


----------------------------------------


Menus:-



File:

     Archive:
             Options for backing up raw data from aircraft, and archiving at BADC
     Files:
             The input files the dataset will use
     Write:
             Write data out as NetCDF


Files:

     View the files to be used as input.  You can add or remove files from the list.  
    
Modules:
     
     View available processing modules
     Hovering over the module name will show the documentation of the module
     Hovering over In and Out will list the input and output parameters
     Clicking on In or Out will open a parameter view showing the relevant parameters
     
Parameters:

     View parameters read in or created by processing.
     The Show button will pop up a window with with a plot or a text description of the data.
     
Process:

     Process data, including reading data in from files


Help:

     Display this help text





                                        

